msgid "Add us as a preferred source on Google"
msgstr "Add us as a preferred source on Google"

msgid "Prefer us on Google"
msgstr "Prefer us on Google"

msgid "What is this?"
msgstr "What is this?"

msgid "You read this blog — which means you value quality content grounded in real experiences. With Google Preferred Sources, tell Google which publishers you trust. Add us and other sources you love, and Google will surface them more in your future search results."
msgstr "You read this blog — which means you value quality content grounded in real experiences. With Google Preferred Sources, tell Google which publishers you trust. Add us and other sources you love, and Google will surface them more in your future search results."

